para_sentences.para_0: Hope you were able to build a foundation in the algorithms topics in this course. Considering the nature of the topics, your learning doesn't stop here. As you would have heard in the message from Alumni that a regular practice would go a long way.
para_sentences.para_1: You would like to explore the resources available online that lists interesting problems in various algorithm topics.
para_sentences.para_2: Please take a few minutes to complete the student learning experience survey for this course. Feedback on your experience in this course matters to us!
